Text: Beat Gold Streak
Wait, what's that bird doing?
Hey! \n I heard you \n can fly.
But just so you know, my \n bird Gold Streak is the \n king of the skies.
Why's this kid \n getting all excited?

Well, I don't really 
 "fly" per se. It's 
 shifting gravity to fall 
 into the sky.
Fall into the sky!?
How adorable, \n he's confused.
It doesn't matter, we \n need to prove who's king \n of the sky.
A little competition, \n eh? Sure, let's do it!
What's going on there?
Waaah!
Old Man: \n Here you go, eat up, eat up.
I won!
Hey, what was that \n at the end?
Rrr... \n That was my \n mortal enemy...
The old man that \n feeds the birds!
He uses a special feed \n to control all of the \n birds in the city.
If it weren't for him, \n I woulda won!
Maybe so, but all that \n matters is results, and \n I got the results.
Enjoy it while it lasts! \n My brother's bird is \n faster than mine!
Okay, let him know I'm \n open to a race whenever \n he wants it.
